{% block body_text %}

Hello %username%!

A password reset was requested for your username. If you did not request a password reset, please notify your administrator and ignore this email.

If you did request to reset your password, please visit {{ url('_password_password_reset', {'token': user.conofirmationToken}) }}%confirmationUrl%

Regards
